1. "VertexGeneratorO" 
                      - gauss (x,y,z) distribution or fixed (0,0,0)
                      - sx, sy, sz - beam sigma ...

2. "VertexGeneratorA" 
                      - with parabolic beam profile
                      - sx, sy, sz - total beam widths ...

3. "VertexGeneratorU" - 
                      - flat (x,y,z) distribution or fixed (0,0,0)
                      - sx, sy, sz - total beam widths ...

